$h2 ${project.name}

This plugin provides the ability to use
[ktlint](https://github.com/shyiko/ktlint) to format and check your source code
against the `ktlint` anti-bikeshedding code style.

$h3 Goals Overview

* [ktlint:format](./format-mojo.html) format your production Kotlin sources
  using `ktlint`.

* [ktlint:testFormat](./testFormat-mojo.html) format your test Kotlin sources
  using `ktlint`.

* [ktlint:lint](./lint-mojo.html) lint your production Kotlin sources using
  `ktlint`.

* [ktlint:testLint](./testLint-mojo.html) lint your test Kotlin sources using
  `ktlint`.

$h3 Usage

General instructions on how to use the ktlint plugin can be found on the
[usage page](./usage.html).

